rm -rf DB/
rm -rf obj
rm -rf bin 
rm -f a.out
rm -f *.o
mkdir -p obj
g++ -c -o obj/plr.o src/plr.cpp -Ofast -pthread -std=c++17 -Iinclude/algos -Iinclude/impl/int -Iinclude/impl/slice -Iinclude/impl/plr -Iinclude/interfaces -Iinclude/types -Iinclude/impl -I./PGM-index/include -Iinclude -DTRACK_STATS=0 -DTRACK_PLR_TRAIN_TIME=0 -DTRUST_ERROR_BOUNDS=0 -DPLR_POS_OFFSET=10 -DPGM_ERROR_BOUND=1 -DUSE_STRING_KEYS=1 -DUSE_INT_128=0 -DUSE_BULK_COPY=1 -DMAX_KEYS_TO_BULK_COPY=1000000 -DTRAIN_RESULT=0
mkdir -p bin/
g++ -Ofast -pthread -std=c++17 obj/plr.o -DTRACK_STATS=0 -DTRACK_PLR_TRAIN_TIME=0 -DTRUST_ERROR_BOUNDS=0 -DPLR_POS_OFFSET=10 -DPGM_ERROR_BOUND=1 -DUSE_STRING_KEYS=1 -DUSE_INT_128=0 -DUSE_BULK_COPY=1 -DMAX_KEYS_TO_BULK_COPY=1000000 -DTRAIN_RESULT=0 src/benchmark.cpp -o bin/benchmark -Iinclude/algos -Iinclude/impl/int -Iinclude/impl/slice -Iinclude/impl/plr -Iinclude/interfaces -Iinclude/types -Iinclude/impl -I./PGM-index/include -Iinclude
